description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready for a new challenge? Do you want to make a difference?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Band 6 Sister/Charge nurse role has become available at Wrightington, Wigan and Leigh Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an exceptional individual who has energy, commitment and enthusiasm to apply for this exciting post within our Intensive Care Unit/ High Dependency Unit (ICU/HDU). The Unit consists of eleven beds which are utilised flexibly to care for both Level 2 HDU and Level 3 ICU patients and currently receive all general critical care admissions from the Trusts wards and the Emergency Care Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role supports the development of both junior and senior nursing staff and strengthens the foundations of the management team. You will need to be a nurse with significant critical care experience and qualifications with developed interpersonal skills and be able to demonstrate a potential for leadership to fulfil this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will require you to work across all areas in the Trust which includes those that are designated as positive, asymptomatic and negative Covid wards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note you will be required to produce original certificates at interview for all qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The interview will be held via Microsoft Teams and we would ask for a 10 minute Poster presentation on&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“What is the biggest challenge as a result of Covid-19 from an ICU team perspective and how will you facilitate a positive approach which is capable of motivating staff?”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The proposed interview date will be the 3rd of December 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameChristine LewisJob titleSisterEmail addresschristine.lewis@wwl.nhs.ukTelephone number01942 822380/2955Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For any further information please contact Christine Lewis or a Senior Sister on ICU/HDU on 01942 822380/2955&lt;/p&gt;
